Global Integrated Range Market Insights
Integrated Range Market Market size was valued at USD 10.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 20.8 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 9.1% from 2024 to 2030.

Integrated Range Market Overview
The global Integrated Range market is currently valued at approximately USD 15.6 billion in 2025, with projections indicating steady growth at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 5.2% through 2030. This growth is driven by the increasing demand for advanced military systems, energy efficiency technologies, and integrated solutions across various sectors such as defense, aerospace, and transportation. The market encompasses integrated range systems that combine both radar and optical technologies to offer enhanced target detection and surveillance capabilities, which are crucial in modern defense and civilian applications.

